Minecraft 1.14 Village & Pillage Update Videos ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7VmhWGNRxKixIX8tWEQn-BnYKE9AaAXk
Minecraft 1.14 the Village & Pillage Update will now have lanterns. These lanterns can be hung from above or placed on a block. Its about time we got a new light source!
